OL,3,CNHS Constitution change could see
OL,4,Ctrans patients treated in rooms on
OL,5,Ctheir own
OL,7,FHospital patients in England will have
OL,8,Fthe right to request to be treated on
OL,9,Fsingle-sex wards under proposed
OL,10,Fchanges to the NHS Constitution, with
OL,11,Ftransgender people placed in rooms on
OL,12,Ftheir own.
OL,14,FThe update "is about putting patients
OL,15,Ffirst", ministers said, and includes
OL,16,Fplans to accommodate requests for same-
OL,17,Fsex intimate care.
