OL,7,FUnder the planned revisions,
OL,8,Ftransgender people could be placed in
OL,9,Fa room on their own if another patient
OL,10,Frequests to be in a single-sex ward.
OL,12,FThis would be permitted under the
OL,13,FEquality Act 2010 when appropriate,
OL,14,F"such as respecting a patient's wish
OL,15,Fto be in a single-sex ward", according
OL,16,Fto the Department of Health and Social
OL,17,FCare.
