OL,7,FIn October, former health secretary
OL,8,FSteve Barclay said he would look into
OL,9,Fchanging the constitution to address
OL,10,Fconcerns about trans women using wards
OL,11,Fintended for biologically female
OL,12,Fpatients.
OL,14,FHealth and Social Care Secretary
OL,15,FVictoria Atkins said: "We want to make
OL,16,Fit abundantly clear that if a patient
OL,17,Fwants same-sex care they should have
OL,18,Faccess to it wherever reasonably
OL,19,Fpossible.
