OL,7,F"It will benefit anyone who needs same-
OL,8,Fsex intimate care in the NHS in
OL,9,FEngland, or who may do so in the
OL,10,Ffuture.
OL,12,F"We can expect an outraged response
OL,13,Ffrom trans rights activists, but this
OL,14,Fis simply a return to common sense,
OL,15,Fand an overdue recognition that
OL,16,Fwomen's wellbeing and safety matter."
OL,18,FHowever, shadow health secretary Wes
OL,19,FStreeting said "rights on paper are
OL,20,Fworthless unless they are delivered in
OL,21,Fpractice".
