OL,7,F"The NHS Constitution already pledges
OL,8,Fthat no patient will have to share an
OL,9,Fovernight ward with patients of the
OL,10,Fopposite sex, but that is not the case
OL,11,Ffor too many patients," he added.
OL,13,F"Labour supports single-sex wards and
OL,14,Fwill provide the staff, investment and
OL,15,Freform the NHS needs to make sure
OL,16,Fevery patient can be cared for safely."
