OL,7,FProfessor Nicola Ranger, chief nursing
OL,8,Fofficer and deputy chief executive of
OL,9,Fthe Royal College of Nursing (RCN),
OL,10,Fsaid: "Patients are already able to
OL,11,Frequest intimate care from a staff
OL,12,Fmember of the same sex, but in an NHS
OL,13,Fmissing tens of thousands of nursing
OL,14,Fstaff it is nigh-on impossible to
OL,15,Faccommodate with any consistency.
OL,17,F"It's also important to recognise that
OL,18,Fnursing staff treat all patients with
OL,19,Fthe utmost respect and
OL,20,Fprofessionalism, no matter their
OL,21,Fgender.
