OL,7,FThe rollout of the escalation process,
OL,8,Falso known as Martha's Rule, started
OL,9,Fearlier this month and follows the
OL,10,Fdeath of 13-year-old Martha Mills in
OL,11,F2021.
OL,13,FShe developed sepsis after suffering a
OL,14,Fpancreatic injury following a fall
OL,15,Ffrom her bike.
OL,17,FMartha's parents, Merope Mills and
OL,18,FPaul Laity, raised concerns about
OL,19,Ftheir daughter's health a number of
OL,20,Ftimes but these were brushed aside.
