OL,7,FLouise Ansari, chief executive of
OL,8,FHealthwatch England, said the
OL,9,Fconstitution "plays a crucial role in
OL,10,Fshaping the culture of our NHS and
OL,11,Fhelping the public to know their
OL,12,Frights".
OL,14,F"Since the NHS Constitution launched,
OL,15,Fit has helped to shift the balance of
OL,16,Fpower from services towards patients
OL,17,Fand their families," she added.
OL,19,F"But, with only a third of people
OL,20,Fknowing their rights, there is still a
OL,21,Flong way to go.
